OL,3,CCumbrian NHS Trust ranked as one of
OL,4,Cthe worst performing services
OL,6,FA Cumbrian NHS Trust say they are
OL,7,F"disappointed" to be ranked as one of
OL,8,Fthe worst performing services in
OL,9,FEngland.
OL,11,FThe first-ever league tables have been
OL,12,Freleased today by NHS England with the
OL,13,Fhope of identifying areas of
OL,14,Funderperformance across the country.
OL,15,FNorth Cumbria Integrated Care has been
OL,16,Fplaced as the fourth worst.
