OL,3,CCumbrian NHS Trust ranked as one of
OL,4,Cthe worst performing services
OL,6,FA spokesperson for NCIC said: "NCICs'
OL,7,Frating is disappointing, but reflects
OL,8,Fthe real structural challenges we face
OL,9,Fas a rural, remote health system, and
OL,10,Fsupports what the new NHS 10-Year Plan
OL,11,Fcalls for in rethinking how care is
OL,12,Fdelivered across the NHS.
OL,14,F"As a Trust, we've stabilised and are
OL,15,Fimproving from where we were four
OL,16,Fyears ago. It is clear that we still
OL,17,Fhave a lot to do.
