OL,3,CCumbrian NHS Trust ranked as one of
OL,4,Cthe worst performing services
OL,6,F"Now we need to go further and faster
OL,7,Fin the months and years ahead. The
OL,8,Fwhole NCIC team share a determined
OL,9,Ffocus on improving performance so that
OL,10,Fprovide better care for our patients.
OL,12,F"We are also reimagining the way we
OL,13,Fdeliver care in North Cumbria `
OL,14,Freviewing our services so that they
OL,15,Fare sustainable and fit for the future.
OL,17,F"We're proud of the fantastic work of
OL,18,Four colleagues. We're clear about what
OL,19,Fstill needs to change. And we're
OL,20,Fambitious for what's ahead."
