OL,3,CCumbrian NHS Trust ranked as one of
OL,4,Cthe worst performing services
OL,6,FUniversity Hospitals of Morecambe Bay
OL,7,FNHS Foundation were ranked mid-table
OL,8,Fon performance. While mental health
OL,9,Fand disability support were ranked
OL,10,Fpoorly at both Cumbria,
OL,11,FNorthumberland, Tyne and Wear NHS
OL,12,FFoundation Trust and Lancashire &
OL,13,FSouth Cumbria NHS Foundation Trust.
OL,15,FThe county's North West Ambulance
OL,16,FService was ranked 1st out of 10
OL,17,Ftrusts across the country.
