OL,3,CCumbrian NHS Trust ranked as one of
OL,4,Cthe worst performing services
OL,6,FThe rankings will be reviewed every
OL,7,Fthree months. The trusts are based on
OL,8,Fa range of measures, including
OL,9,Ffinances, patient access to care,
OL,10,Foperation waiting times, A&E, and
OL,11,Fambulance response times.
OL,13,FThe league table is categorised into
OL,14,Ffour segments, with the first
OL,15,Freflecting the best performers and the
OL,16,Ffourth highlighting the worst.
OL,18,FTop performers will be given greater
OL,19,Ffreedoms and investment, the
OL,20,FDepartment of Health and Social Care
OL,21,F(DHSC) said.
