OL,3,CCumbrian NHS Trust ranked as one of
OL,4,Cthe worst performing services
OL,6,FHigher standards will also be set for
OL,7,Fleaders, tying pay and performance
OL,8,Ftogether under new plans by the DHSC.
OL,10,FSenior managers who are persistently
OL,11,Franked poorly could see their pay
OL,12,Fdocked, while NHS leaders will have
OL,13,Fextra pay incentives to improve NHS
OL,14,Ftrusts.
OL,16,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting says
OL,17,Fquarterly rankings will identify where
OL,18,Furgent support is needed and help end
OL,19,Fthe "postcode lottery" of care for
OL,20,Fpatients.
